            <fr:title text="Hausdorff Space">Hausdorff Space</fr:title>
            <fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <html:p>
A <fr:link href="/gtop-0002/" title="Topological Space" uri="https://boatnotabot.com/gtop-0002/" display-uri="gtop-0002" type="local">topological space</fr:link> is <html:strong>Hausdorff</html:strong> if for every pair of distinct points therein there exist a <fr:link href="/gtop-000F/" title="Neighborhood" uri="https://boatnotabot.com/gtop-000F/" display-uri="gtop-000F" type="local">neighbourhood</fr:link> of each point that are disjoint from each other.
</html:p>
          </fr:mainmatter>
