            <fr:title text="Radon Measure">Radon Measure</fr:title>
            <fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <html:p>
A <html:strong>Radon measure</html:strong> on a <fr:link href="/gtop-000O/" title="Locally Compact Space" uri="https://boatnotabot.com/gtop-000O/" display-uri="gtop-000O" type="local">locally compact</fr:link> <fr:link href="/gtop-000B/" title="Hausdorff Space" uri="https://boatnotabot.com/gtop-000B/" display-uri="gtop-000B" type="local">Hausdorff space</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[X]]></fr:tex> is a <fr:link href="/gtop-000C/" title="Borel Measure" uri="https://boatnotabot.com/gtop-000C/" display-uri="gtop-000C" type="local">Borel measure</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mu ]]></fr:tex> satisfying:
</html:p>
            <html:ol><html:li><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mu (K) < \infty ]]></fr:tex> for every <fr:link href="/gtop-0008/" title="Compactness" uri="https://boatnotabot.com/gtop-0008/" display-uri="gtop-0008" type="local">compact</fr:link> set <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[K \subseteq  X]]></fr:tex>.</html:li>
<html:li><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mu ]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link href="/gtop-000D/" title="Outer Regularity" uri="https://boatnotabot.com/gtop-000D/" display-uri="gtop-000D" type="local">outer regular</fr:link> on all <fr:link href="/gtop-000L/" title="Borel Set" uri="https://boatnotabot.com/gtop-000L/" display-uri="gtop-000L" type="local">Borel sets</fr:link>.</html:li>
<html:li><fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mu ]]></fr:tex> is <fr:link href="/gtop-000E/" title="Inner Regularity" uri="https://boatnotabot.com/gtop-000E/" display-uri="gtop-000E" type="local">inner regular</fr:link> on all <fr:link href="/gtop-0005/" title="Open Set" uri="https://boatnotabot.com/gtop-0005/" display-uri="gtop-0005" type="local">open sets</fr:link>.</html:li></html:ol>
          </fr:mainmatter>
        </fr:tree>
