            <fr:title text="Locally Compact Space">Locally Compact Space</fr:title>
            <fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon>
          </fr:frontmatter>
          <fr:mainmatter>
            <html:p>
A <fr:link href="/gtop-0002/" title="Topological Space" uri="https://boatnotabot.com/gtop-0002/" display-uri="gtop-0002" type="local">topological space</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[X]]></fr:tex> is <html:strong>locally compact</html:strong> if every point <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[x \in  X]]></fr:tex> has a <fr:link href="/gtop-000F/" title="Neighborhood" uri="https://boatnotabot.com/gtop-000F/" display-uri="gtop-000F" type="local">neighbourhood</fr:link> contained in a <fr:link href="/gtop-0008/" title="Compactness" uri="https://boatnotabot.com/gtop-0008/" display-uri="gtop-0008" type="local">compact</fr:link> subset of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[X]]></fr:tex>.
</html:p>
          </fr:mainmatter>
        </fr:tree>
